{
  "stem": "833.1",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "One grows up twice as fast in such times of real trouble.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You see, the security that we felt so strongly was suddenly broken.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We didn't know, is-- has Father to go to war?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or is he going to stay home?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He was-- at that time, he was technical director of the-- possibly, I think it was the last largest central European industrial combine.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He had to-- under his leadership, there were 52 plants all over Austria.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And one-- one third of the year, he was always out traveling.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he couldn't-- they-- they wouldn't let him go to war.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But he didn't know, because one day, he had appeared in uniform.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so therefore, our interest into-- in-- in what is happening, that was so strongly focused to our own life, to the life at home, was suddenly projected entirely to the world.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "That means we grew up much faster.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "A boy, in-- let's say, in the winter of 1914, '15, could not be compared to a boy of the same age today because we were living with-- with the history that was being made.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And in addition to that, in the summer when-- when before the war was really started, when the diplomatic stupidities were being enacted, there was a young poet who accompanied us-- our governess and all we children-- when we were-- when we walked every morning to Schonbrunn.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We didn't go to the country because my father was afraid of-- of the war coming up, that we should be at home.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was a-- he was a real radical-- a poet who saw his time and who explained to me in no uncertain terms what the powers are, what really drives [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he was really right.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
